OL,3,CMan who received first pig kidney
OL,4,Ctransplant dies
OL,6,FThe first recipient of a genetically
OL,7,Fmodified pig kidney transplant has
OL,8,Fdied nearly two months after he
OL,9,Funderwent the procedure, the hospital
OL,10,Fwhich carried out the operation has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FRichard "Rick" Slayman had the
OL,14,Ftransplant at Massachusetts General
OL,15,FHospital in March at the age of 62.
OL,16,FSurgeons said they believed the pig
OL,17,Fkidney would last for at least two
OL,18,Fyears.
