OL,6,FThe transplant team at Massachusetts
OL,7,FGeneral Hospital said in a statement
OL,8,Fit was deeply saddened by Mr Slayman's
OL,9,Fpassing, and added there was not any
OL,10,Findication that he died as a result of
OL,11,Fthe transplant.
OL,13,FMr Slayman, from Massachusetts, was
OL,14,Fthe first living person to have the
OL,15,Fprocedure.
OL,17,FSlayman had a kidney transplant at the
OL,18,Fhospital in 2018, but he had to go
OL,19,Fback on dialysis last year when it
OL,20,Fshowed signs of failure.
