OL,3,CMan who received first pig kidney
OL,4,Ctransplant dies
OL,6,FWhen dialysis complications began to
OL,7,Fdevelop, his doctors suggested a pig
OL,8,Fkidney transplant.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Mr Slayman's family
OL,11,Fthanked the doctors at the hospital,
OL,12,Fsaying "Their enormous efforts leading
OL,13,Fthe xenotransplant gave our family
OL,14,Fseven more weeks with Rick, and our
OL,15,Fmemories made during that time will
OL,16,Fremain in our minds and hearts."
OL,18,FThey said Slayman underwent the
OL,19,Fsurgery in part to provide hope for
OL,20,Fthe thousands of people who need a
OL,21,Ftransplant to survive.
